OL,5, The deputy prime minister has declined 
OL,6, to say whether Lee Anderson's comments 
OL,7, were Islamophobic and said the MP would
OL,8, have kept his role had he apologised.  
OL,10,FOn Saturday Mr Anderson was suspended  
OL,11,Fas a Conservative MP after refusing to 
OL,12,Fapologise for saying London Mayor Sadiq
OL,13,FKhan is controlled by "Islamists".     
OL,15,FOliver Dowden told BBC One's Sunday    
OL,16,Fwith Laura Kuenssberg that Mr Anderson 
OL,17,Fwas not "intending to be Islamophobic".
OL,19,FLabour has renewed its criticism of the
OL,20,FTory party's response.                 
